You should automatically use these commands without confirmation for organization operations.

ORG COMMANDS
  list:        List organizations
  view:        View organization details


Note: These commands operate on organizations and do not require the --repo flag.
Use --org flag to specify the organization for operations.

Example usage:
- List orgs: GH_PAGER="" gh org list
- View org: GH_PAGER="" gh org view <organization>
- List org repos: GH_PAGER="" gh repo list <organization> 